### ANIMATIONS & TRANSITIONS

- Panel switch: `opacity 0 → 1` + `translateY(12px → 0)`, duration ~500ms, ease cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1)
- Panel → Carousel: same fade/slide transition
- Carousel → Panel (back): reverse
- Countdown: ticks every 1 second via `setInterval`, cleared on unmount
- Timeline dot selection: smooth dot size + fill transition ~300ms
- Hover on category cards: ~220ms border + background transition
- No janky layout shifts. All transitions use `position: absolute` panels overlaid in the stage so layout never reflows.

---

### RESPONSIVENESS

| Breakpoint | Behavior |
|---|---|
| Mobile < 768px | Single column, all centered, carousel shows 1 + half card, timeline nodes slightly smaller, countdown wraps if needed |
| Tablet 768–1024px | Carousel shows 2 + half cards |
| Desktop > 1024px | Carousel shows 3 + half cards, full layout as designed |

Use CSS media queries or Tailwind responsive prefixes — match whatever the site uses.

