### WHAT NOT TO DO

- Do not use any color, font, or spacing value that isn't from the site's design tokens
- Do not use `<img>` if the site uses `next/image`
- Do not use `<a href>` if the site uses `next/link`
- Do not install any new npm packages — use only what is already in `package.json`
- Do not left-align anything — everything is centered
- Do not add a heading above the carousel
- Do not add pagination dots or arrows to the carousel
- Do not make the category cards navigate to a new page — they open the carousel inline
- Do not forget to clear the countdown `setInterval` in the `useEffect` cleanup

